<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[التسهيد]</span>: سَهَّده: أي أرّقه.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>قال <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وبِتُّ كما بات السليممسهَّدا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
