<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[التَّسهيم]</span>: بُرْدٌ مُسَهَّم: أي مخطط.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">والمُسَهَّم:</span> الساهم وهو الضامر.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
